								class Attribute2
								{
									property="ModuleCreateDiaryRecord_F_Description";
									expression="_this setVariable ['Description',_value,true];";
									class Value
									{
										class data
										{
											singleType="STRING";
											value="<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>=== SITUATION ===</font>         " \n "<br/><br/>  " \n "A few weeks has passed since the US deployed is fleet to chernarus, the attack on svetloyarsk and taking of krasno airfield has been vital in securing more grounds. Remnants of CDF forces have been active in providing recon and intel on chDKZ movements, They have been able to pin point multiple locations with heavy traffic from chDKZ.   " \n "<br/><br/> " \n "High command has tasked USMC Force Recon and aviation branch with raiding 4 locations. We have reason to believe their holding our troops captive and are actively torturing them.  " \n "<br/><br/> " \n "There's chances you'll find some hostages dead on arrival, You are required to bring body bags for those situations, High command wants you to bring our boys back at all costs. " \n "<br/><br/> " \n "<font face='PuristaBold' color='#fce300' size='15'>=== MISSION ===</font>   " \n "<br/><br/> " \n "Your task force will be sent in for search and rescue along with additional objectives. " \n "<br/><br/> " \n "Objectives are as follows, Rescue hostages, Capture Ivan Petrikov, Destroy Ammo Cache. " \n "<br/><br/> " \n "Godspeed, High command Out.";
										};
									};
								};
